solidbase.util
Class CSVTokenizer

java.lang.Object
  solidbase.util.CSVTokenizer

public class CSVTokenizer
extends Object

This is a tokenizer for CSV. It maintains the current line number, and it ignores whitespace.

Author:
René M. de Bloois
